YEAH, IT'S GOT
A 6.1 HEMI, A V-8,

00:11.010 --> 00:13.808
470 HORSEPOWER AT THE CRANK.

00:13.840 --> 00:16.149
IF YOU ASK, SHE'LL ANSWER.

00:16.180 --> 00:17.977
NOT TO MENTION
IT'S A TOTAL CHICK MAGNET.

00:18.010 --> 00:20.478
LEAST OF MY CONCERNS.
I'M OFF THE MARKET.

00:20.520 --> 00:23.648
UH, CAN YOU--
