I ASKED YOU TO STEP OUT
FROM BEHIND THE COUNTER.

08:11.050 --> 08:12.984
SHOW ME YOUR HANDS.

08:13.020 --> 08:14.851
HEY! HEY! HEY!

08:14.890 --> 08:17.188
HEY! STAND UP!
I SAID, "STAND UP!"

08:17.230 --> 08:18.424
HEY, WHAT'S GOING ON?
GET OUTSIDE NOW!

08:18.460 --> 08:20.849
(radio static)
1518. POSSIBLE 10-89
IN PROGRESS.

08:20.900 --> 08:22.151
CORNER OF GLEN ROAD
AND HOWARD.
(static)

08:22.200 --> 08:23.326
GET OUTSIDE NOW!

08:23.370 --> 08:25.793
OUTSIDE! MOVE! STAND UP!

08:25.830 --> 08:28.037
PUT YOUR HANDS ABOVE YOUR HEAD
AND STAND UP SLOWLY.

08:28.070 --> 08:31.460
PUT YOUR HANDS ABOVE YOUR HEAD
AND STAND UP SLOWLY.

