08:41.020 --> 08:42.044
(static)

08:42.080 --> 08:43.945
(radio chatter)
YOU HIT?

08:43.990 --> 08:45.639
(holster rustles)
DOV, ARE YOU HIT?

08:45.690 --> 08:47.817
(gurgling)

08:47.860 --> 08:51.421
(panﬁng)

